narkreward:
NArk Bonus: Initially, the airdrop weight of each address is 1 by default, but each address can get the airdrop bonus by expanding its NArk. NArk contains the Parent Block Address(PBA) and Uncle Block Address(UBA). The specific addition method is as follows : 
Each PBA can add 0.3 airdrop weight to the account, and the maximum added weight is 1.5; 
Each UBA can add 0.1 airdrop weight to the account, and the maximum added weight is 2.5;

